{"tid":1393632,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍某中學田徑小飛人發表偉論","createTime":"2019-08-01T07:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T07:43:55.000Z","uid":228349,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e16e992e33d5c8f78e987c8ac8ab6599981e5d4b","tid":1393632,"uid":228349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:04:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">7月30號又一個不眠夜，天水圍某中學既學生比狗捉左，同一時間該中學18-19年剛畢業既畢業生發表偉論，呢位同學平日都好自豪自己屋企有本紅簿仔，對中國大陸十分嚮往。<br />\n <br />\n佢平時嘅言行除左自大左少少，同學都盡量包容佢，不過佢當晚嘅言論實左難在不能接受，我諗唔到點解佢可以口出狂言，佢講嘅野已經唔單止係邏輯上有問題，更加係思想上有問題。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q07Bsdo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ07Bsdo.jpg&h=136c509d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4dGCbE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4dGCbE4.jpg&h=624f21ac&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/64JXV6L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F64JXV6L.jpg&h=4e50c766&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fJHRf6M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfJHRf6M.jpg&h=83843872&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n己經唔係立場問題，而係唔負責既言論，我以為只有年長一輩、籃絲、送中人士先會有呢啲諗法，但佢講嘅野顛覆左我對我地年青人嘅印象，邊可能估到一個同我地接受相同教育、係相同環境下成長嘅人會有錦嘅思想。<br />\n #冇話要政治正確 #Sorry for 1999<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"c7f0fb249331c0cfef11d467c5d6f6c6c4d48326","tid":1393632,"uid":117532,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:09:51.000Z","msg":"叫自己做stupid又要講埋啲懶係眾人皆醉我獨醒既野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想點撚樣呀?"},{"pid":"81bf11381697d456d48dd39523782188ee1c5162","tid":1393632,"uid":228349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T07:14:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"09062842dde5bc4969e35e5858c51990d597632b","tid":1393632,"uid":228349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201